## Gate ledger  (DoD core rows + active pack rows — each ✅ needs an evidence pointer; ⬜/🔴 are honest)
| Gate | Status | Evidence |
|------|--------|----------|
| Build/validate green | ✅/⬜/🔴 | <→cmd #> |
| Dedicated commit + slice id (or NO-GIT flagged) | … | <hash> |
| **CI green — machine-read at merge** (the merge runs VIA `merge-pr`, which reads the checks API; never piped/watched output) | … | gate output |
| Migration reversible + applies-clean-on-fresh-DB + rollback rehearsed | … | … |
| Failure paths → honest error, no false success | … | … |
| <pack rows: RBAC/authz · evals+grounding · canonical · money-idempotent> | … | … |
> v4 note: the old "CI green: runs at PR time" deferral row is DELETED — deferring the CI check to "later" is
> exactly how a red CI merged once (the merge gate now owns this check mechanically).

## FAIL history  (kept in-doc — a failed run is part of the record, never overwritten)
